│  leave days per year.                   │
│  Unused leave cannot be carried         │
│  forward to the next year.              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

A user asks:

```
❓ How many paid leave days does an employee get?
```

**Without RAG:**

```
The AI guesses based on general knowledge:
"Typically companies offer 10–15 days..."   ← WRONG / HALLUCINATED
```

**With RAG:**

```
