## ⚖️ RAG vs No RAG

| Scenario | Without RAG | With RAG |
|---------|------------|---------|
| **Knowledge source** | Training data only (fixed date) | Your uploaded documents (always fresh) |
| **Private company data** | ❌ Cannot access | ✅ Fully accessible |
| **Accuracy on specific facts** | Risk of hallucination | Grounded in real text |
| **Knowledge cutoff** | Hard cutoff (e.g. 2024) | No cutoff — upload new docs anytime |
| **Source traceability** | ❌ Cannot cite sources | ✅ Can cite exact document & page |
| **Custom domains** | Generic knowledge only | Domain-specific (legal, medical, HR, etc.) |
| **Cost** | One inference call | Slightly higher (retrieval + inference) |

