## 🧬 Embedding Models

Embeddings are the heart of RAG. They convert text to meaning-preserving vectors.

```
How similarity works in vector space:

  "machine learning" ●
                      \
                       \  close distance = similar meaning
                        \
  "deep learning"    ●──┘

                                            ● "cooking recipes"
                                              (far away = different meaning)
```

**Choosing the right embedding model:**

```
Small project / prototype:
  → all-MiniLM-L6-v2  (free, fast, good quality)

Production accuracy needed:
  → BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5  (open source, high accuracy)

Using OpenAI already:
  → text-embedding-3-small  (cheap, 1536-dim)

Multilingual documents:
  → multilingual-e5-large  (supports 100+ languages)
```

