## ✅ Summary

RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) works in three simple stages:

```
  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │                                                          │
  │   1. STORE         Upload & index your documents         │
  │      ────────────────────────────────────────────────    │
  │      Documents → Extract → Chunk → Embed → Vector DB     │
  │                                                          │
  │   2. RETRIEVE      Find relevant information             │
  │      ────────────────────────────────────────────────    │
  │      Question → Embed → Similarity Search → Top Chunks   │
  │                                                          │
  │   3. GENERATE      Produce an accurate answer            │
  │      ────────────────────────────────────────────────    │
  │      Chunks + Question → LLM Prompt → Final Answer       │
  │                                                          │
  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**RAG is the bridge between your private knowledge and AI intelligence.**

It turns any LLM into a domain expert on your own data — without retraining, without hallucination, and without a knowledge cutoff.

